str2: In order that, so that. Probably from the same as the former part of heautou; in order that.

str2: To take advantage of, overreach, defraud. From pleonektes; to be covetous, i.e. to over-reach.
For. A primary particle; properly, assigning a reason.

str2: To do not know, be ignorant of, sometimes with the idea of willful ignorance.

str2: He, she, it, they, them, same. From the particle au; the reflexive pronoun self, used of the third person, and of the other persons.
From noieo; a perception, i.e. Purpose, or the intellect, disposition, itself.
